ass=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 207.09141274238px;\">\n<p class=\"a5\" style=\" text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"structures structure-3\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">{#3}Буйруқ рақами</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 207.09141274238px;\">\n<p class=\"a5\" style=\" margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"structures structure-4\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">{#4}Буйруқ қабул қилинган жой</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Ишга қабул қилиш тўғрисида</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">1. </span><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-weight: bold;\">{#6}Ходимнинг фамилияси, исми, отасининг исми</span><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"> -</span> <span class=\"structures structure-7\" style=\"\">{#7}Ходим ишга қабул қилинаётга сана</span>дан <span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"\">{#8}Ходим ишга қабул қилинаётган ташкилот номи</span>га – автотранспорт ҳайдовчиси лавозимига ишга қабул қилинсин.</p>\n<p>2. Ташкилот балансидаги давлат рақами <span class=\"structures structure-9\" style=\"\">{#9}Ходимга бириктирилаётган автомашина рақам белгиси</span> бўлган <span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"\">{#10}Ходимга бириктирилаётган автомашина русуми</span>русумли хизмат автомашина ҳайдовчига унинг моддий жавобгарлиги остида бириктирилсин.</p>\n<p>3. Ходимга ойлик маош штатлар жадвалига мувофиқ белгилансин.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">Асос:</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"> Ўзбекистон Республикаси Меҳнат кодексининг 127-моддаси ва ходим билан тузилган меҳнат шартномаси.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<table style=\"border: 0px solid; border-spacing: 0; \">\n<tr>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 203.50138504155px;\">\n<p><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"\">{#11}Буйруқ чиқарган шахснинг лавозими</span></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 188.21052631579px;\">\n<p>____________</p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 228.43213296399px;\">\n<p><span class=\"structures structure-12\" style=\"\">{#12}Буйруқ чиқарган шахснинг Ф.И.О.си</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" 